<plot>Andy (Andy Clyde) and Charlie (Charles Rogers) are two failed prospectors who return to their shack/home at the city dump and find it occupied by a young boy with a lame leg (Charles Bates) and his older sister (Glora Marlen.) In order to get the money to pay for Jimmy's operation, Andy and Charlie buy a map to a gold mine from a con man (Robert Williams) and dig their way into the bank vault.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?013315</url></doc>
